#Settings
option.FOG=Fog
option.FOG.comment=Enables/disables fog rendering.

option.shadowMapResolution=Shadow Resolution
option.shadowMapResolution.comment=Use higher values for higher quality shadows. High performance impact!

option.sunPathRotation=Shadow Rotation Offset
option.sunPathRotation.comment=Changes the angle of the sun. This is your fault Builderb0y!

option.shadowDistance=Shadow Distance
option.shadowDistance.comment=Changes how far shadows are rendered. Higher values mean higher quality shadows at farther distances. Smaller values mean higher quality shadows at shorter distances.

option.TRANSPARENT_SHADOWS=Shadows on Transparents
option.TRANSPARENT_SHADOWS.comment=Whether shadows are cast on transparent blocks (water, glass, etc.). High performance impact!

option.GRASS_SHADOWS=Plant Shadows
option.GRASS_SHADOWS.comment=Whether plants cast shadows.

option.SHADOW_STRENGTH=Shadow Strength
option.SHADOW_STRENGTH.comment=Controls how dark shadows are.

option.PCSS=Percentage Closer Soft Shadows
option.PCSS.comment=Makes shadows more realistic softening them as they get farther from the caster (PCSS). High performance impact!

option.RANDOM_ROTATION=Grain
option.RANDOM_ROTATION.comment=Helps to make blurred shadow edges smoother. Adds noise, but removes banding. Medium performance impact.

option.PCSS_SAMPLE_COUNT=PCSS Quality
option.PCSS_SAMPLE_COUNT.comment=Higher values means higher quality PCSS. Medium performance impact.

option.PCF_SAMPLE_COUNT=Filter Quality
option.PCF_SAMPLE_COUNT.comment=Higher values means higher quality filtering. Makes shadow edges appear smoother. Medium performance impact.

option.LIGHT_SIZE=Light Size
option.LIGHT_SIZE.comment=Adjusts the assumed size of the sun. Higher values means softer shadows. Only effective with PCSS enabled!

option.MIN_PENUMBRA_SIZE=Minimum Blur
option.MIN_PENUMBRA_SIZE.comment=Minimum size of blurred shadow edges. 0 means completely sharp shadows. Only effective with PCSS enabled!

option.VANILLA_SUN=Vanilla Sun
option.VANILLA_SUN.comment=Whether to use the vanilla sun or circular sun.

option.VANILLA_MOON=Vanilla Moon
option.VANILLA_MOON.comment=Whether to use the vanilla moon or circular moon.

option.SUN_POSITION_FIX=Sun Position Fix
option.SUN_POSITION_FIX.comment=Used to fix the position of the sun in sky calculation. Only necessary when running at low frame rates (less than 30).

option.WAVING_DEADBUSH=Waving Deadbush
option.WAVING_DEADBUSH.comment=Waving Deadbush

option.WAVING_LEAVES=Waving Leaves
option.WAVING_LEAVES.comment=Waving Leaves

